; Sakura Shape Audit — 2026-07-14
; Automated per-verb classification against Sakura-shape doctrine.
; Reviewer: shape-audit-lane (script-driven, heuristic).
;
; Verdict legend:
;   sakura-shaped         — examples fit Sakura world; keep as-is
;   console-shape-legit   — fantasy-console verb, console-shape is CORRECT
;   console-shape-leaking — non-console verb whose examples leaked console idioms; RESHAPE
;   r7rs-violation        — example uses non-R7RS forms (funcall/call-cc/defmacro/etc)
;   intent-unclear        — name+args do not clarify intent; ASK ALFRED

